{{Top|leg}}
'''Croig's Fix-It Barn''' was a repair shop located on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Nam Chorios/Legends|Nam Chorios]], in the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Hweg Shul]]. The facility's owner, the [[Duros/Legends|Duros]] [[Croig Jacamden]], took pride in it being the biggest repair shop in Hweg Shul, and consequently on the entire planet, since it encompassed about thirty repair bays.

==History==
While searching for his love, [[Callista Ming]], in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] took a temporary job as a mechanic at the Fix-It Barn in order to better conduct his search.

